  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK876">
<l>tēṟiṉun tēṟā viṭiṉu maḻiviṉkaṭ</l>
<l>ṭēṟāṉ pakāaṉ viṭal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though (one's foe is) aware or not of one's misfortune one should act so as neither to join nor separate (from him).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
